stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR

  state "Running sandbox" as Running
  state "Paused sandbox" as Paused
  state "Snapshot created" as Stored
  state "Restored sandbox" as Restored

  Running --> Paused: pause into snapshot
  Running --> Stored: create snapshot
  Paused --> Restored: restore snapshot
  Stored --> Restored: restore snapshot

  note right of Stored
    Source sandbox stays running
  end note
